a.popular-categories-card(href=category.url)
	.popular-categories-card__wrap
		.popular-categories-card__img
			img(src='#{media_url}#{category.image}', alt=category.name)
		.popular-categories-card__content
			.popular-categories-card__title=category.name
			.popular-categories-card__link
				| Перейти
				+icon('arrow-right')